[SN]TITLE[SN]
US space agency Nasa are on a mission to find a 'planet protector'

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
US space agency Nasa are looking for someone to be a planetary protection officer.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
3 August 2017 Last updated at 16:06 BST
They want someone who can protect the Earth from pollution, and maybe even aliens!
It's a big responsibility and pays a lot of money.
Find out if you could be the next planet protector...
